info.author: Maciej Wilczyński
classifiers: Topic :: Software Development :: Libraries :: Python Modules
info.name: safe-init
info.summary: Safe Init is a Python library that enhances AWS Lambda functions with advanced error handling, logging, monitoring, and resilience features, providing comprehensive observability and reliability for serverless applications.
